      <a href="/agent-ready-repository/">Start here →</a>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>AGENTS.md</h3>
      <p>Use durable repository instructions instead of repeating prompts in every session.</p>
      <a href="/agents-md-template/">Use the template →</a>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Harness engineering</h3>
